In Eclipse 3.3M6 + GEF 3.3M6 (Windows XP), try to open a diagram editor in japanese NL (ja locale) throws an exception because of com.ibm.icu plugin (com.ibm.icu_3.6.0.20061215) missing resource bundle property. Exception throws only in japanese NL and all other locales diagram editor opens fine. If this defect is fixed in latest version, please provide information.
